00:00:36.770 --> 00:02:10.789
How to Change the Cord Lock and Idlers on
a Woven Wood Shade

00:02:10.789 --> 00:02:28.050
Remove the shade and place it on a flat surface
Remove the tassels

00:02:28.050 --> 00:02:36.590
Pull the cords through the cord lock and idlers
Remove the old idlers and cord lock

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:45.130
Install the new idlers and cord lock
Make sure the cord lock is oriented the same

00:02:45.130 --> 00:02:53.680
way to insure it locks in the same direction
Rethread the strings back through the idlers

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:58.480
Thread the wire restring tool through the
cord lock

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:05.950
Pull one of the cords through
Repeat for the other cords making sure they

00:03:05.950 --> 00:03:14.500
are separated through the cord lock as shown
If the strings are frayed, hold them together

00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:18.230
evenly and trim
Tie on the tassels

00:03:18.230 --> 00:03:19.830
Test your repair

